               <p>I am a <rs id="t17801018-27-viclabel142" type="occupation">gun-stocker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17801018-27-victim303 t17801018-27-viclabel142"></join> by trade. On Saturday the 9th of September I went out to tea. I placed a tenant saw upon a bench in my master's shop. I was absent an hour and an half; when I was returning to the shop 
               <persName id="t17801018-27-person305">
                  John
                   Pinkerton
               <interp inst="t17801018-27-person305" type="surname" value="Pinkerton"></interp>
