             met me; he said he had seen the saw taken away. I saw it the same day in the possession of Crocker. It is my property.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17801018-27-person306">
                  JOHN
                   PINKERTON
               <interp inst="t17801018-27-person306" type="surname" value="PINKERTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17801018-27-person306" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
