                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>Coming out of my master's shop, I observed the saw in the prisoner's hand; he laid it down upon seeing me; after that he went away with his coat buttoned, and his arm under his coat. I could not see the saw, but I suspected he had stolen it; after he was gone I went into the shop, and missed it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17801018-27-person307">
                  ANDREW
                   CROCKER
               <interp inst="t17801018-27-person307" type="surname" value="CROCKER"></interp>
