                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>On the 9th of September, about four in the afternoon , the prisoner brought this saw to me. I lent him two shillings upon it; he said it was his own property.</p>
               <p>(The saw was produced in court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I know nothing at all of it.</p>
